Tim Kerbavaz is the Special Event Support Technical Director for Academic Technology Services at UC Davis.  He is a graduate of UC Davis (A.B. Technocultural Studies, Winter 13) and is the former Productions Coordinator for the ASUCD Entertainment Council and the former president of the Technocultural Studies Club

Tim provides live sound and event production services in the Davis area with his business http://www.talonent.com Talon Entertainment
More information about Tim can be found at his website http://www.kerbavaz.com/
